            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Cartula de Franciano. In nomine domini nostri Iesu Christi. Anno ab
                        incarnatione eius millesimo centesimo vicegimo primo, mense martio,
                        indictione quarta Xa. Manifestus sum ego <persName key="#Count"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/96">Ildebrandus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comes</rs> filius <persName key="#Count"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/97">Raineri</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comitis</rs>, qui professus sum lege viv[ere …] et
                            <persName key="#Countess" ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/98"
                            >Maximilla</persName>
                        <rs key="#Countess">comitissa</rs> iugales et <rs key="#Countess"
                            >comitissam</rs>
                        <persName key="#Countess" ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/99"
                            >Lupa</persName> qualiter comuniter et consentientes promittimus
                        venerabili <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/103"
                            >Mauro</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs> stipulanti quod ab hac hora in antea nos, nec
                        alii per nos, nec nostri hered[es …]bimus adversus <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterium</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/juridical_persons/78"
                            key="#Monasteries">Sancti Quilici </orgName>nec adversus suos rectores
                        nec adversus aliquem vestro nomine possidentes agemus, nominatim de
                        medietate omnium <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terrarum</rs>, quas olim
                        abuistis et tenuistis, vel alii per vo[s, a co]mite Rainerio et a <rs
                            key="#Countess">comitissa</rs>
                        <persName key="#Countess" ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/101"
                            >Adalasia</persName> in <placeName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/89"
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Castle">Franciano</placeName>, sicuti in ipsa
                        cartula legitur, et finibus circumdata, et etiam de medietate de ipso <rs
                            key="#Castle">castellare</rs>. Et si apparuerit ullum datum aut factum
                        vel ali[a da]tio vel obligatio, quam nos in aliquam partem fecissemus et nos
                        inde vos defendere non potuerimus ab omnibus hominibus, promittimus tibi
                        Mauro abbati et tuis successoribus stipulanti componere penam quinquaginta
                        librarum Lucensium et post penam solutam hoc pactum maneat firmum verbis
                        subnixum, quia inter nos taliter convenimus. Launehild, idest meritum,
                        recipimus a te prefato abbate, ut hec obbligatio valeat et firma permaneat.
                        Actum in <placeName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/87"
                            >Suvereto</placeName>. Signa manuum Ildebrandi comitis et Lupe comitisse
                        et Maximille iugalis, qui queve hoc pactum verbis subnixum scribere
                        rogaverunt. Signa manuum <persName key="#Viscount"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/104">Rugeri</persName>
                        <rs key="#Viscount">vicecomitis</rs> filii <persName>Ildibrandi</persName>
                        et <persName>Wlpelli</persName> filii <persName>Perli</persName> et
                            <persName>Berardini</persName> filii <persName>Petri Crassi</persName>
                        et <persName>Malpilli</persName> filii eius et <persName>Rainerii</persName>
                        filii <persName>Rufinelli</persName> et <persName>Tancredi</persName> filii
                            <persName>Ugiccionis Berardoni</persName> et
                            <persName>Salarii</persName> filii <persName>Walfredi</persName> de
                            <placeName>Tremali</placeName> et <persName>Wazonis</persName> de
                            <placeName>Monte Liverenti</placeName> et <persName>Widonis</persName>
                        de <placeName>Monticulo</placeName> testium. Maximilla comitissa filia <rs
                            key="#Count">comitis</rs>
                        <persName key="#Count">Rogerii</persName> confirmavit hoc in <placeName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/88">Malliano</placeName>, testibus
                            <persName>Rugerio</persName> de <placeName>Biserno</placeName> et
                            <persName>Widone</persName> et <persName>Banbarino</persName>. || Ego
                            <persName key="#Notary #Judge">Aimerigus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> et <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> domini
                        inperatoris post tradita complevi et dedi. </ab>
